{"data":[{"date":"10:23 03/07","title":"Thua \u0111au Brazil, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico tr\u00e1ch nhau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/thua-dau-brazil-nguoi-mexico-trach-nhau-khong-het-minh-o-vong-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Rafael Marquez ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201ccon ng\u00e1o \u1ed9p\u201d n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brazil nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, t\u1eeb tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh gi\u00e0 d\u01a1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u00e1i d\u1edbp l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico El Tri tr\u00e1ch nhau v\u00ec m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico El Tri tr\u00e1ch nhau v\u00ec m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/thua-dau-brazil-nguoi-mexico-trach-nhau-khong-het-minh-o-vong-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh khi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u201cnh\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Rafael Marquez sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-mexico-463-190202.html\" target=\"_blank\">d\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico</span>: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0\u1edfng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd b\u00e1u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan v\u00e0 b\u1ecf d\u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Brazil, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap Selecao nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. \u1ede v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba l\u00e0m n\u00ean cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-neymar-toa-sang-giup-brazil-ha-mexico-20-421-190231.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n d\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico\u00a0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-20-mexico-gia-tri-cua-neymar-khong-chi-o-nhung-ban-thang-421-190245.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico: Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-20-mexico-xung-danh-nguoi-dan-duong-cua-world-cup-421-190244.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico: X\u1ee9ng danh \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#111111\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#111111\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"847","checkdouble":"190256"},{"date":"09:29 03/07","title":"\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t \"Samurai xanh\" c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 5 (cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng) \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00eam qua, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh m\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-2, gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lukaku g\u00f3p v\u00e0o b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lukaku g\u00f3p v\u00e0o b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/3-thomas-meunier-makes-his-run-copy-1530569049657107471436.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Meunier.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKevin De Bruyne ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, Meunier c\u0103ng ngang cho Chadli b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea1ng l\u1edbn trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois b\u1eaft d\u00ednh tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Kevin De Bruyne d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c nhanh v\u1ec1 n\u1eeda s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia. Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hai b\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Song t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho B\u1ec9 khi Lukaku ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKevin De Bruyne qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m b\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Meunier. Sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung ra nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00edch ng\u1eafm l\u00e0 ai?\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku tiep tuc chay cho hut nguoi.\" title=\"Lukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/4-meunier-crosses-the-ball-in-copy-1530569049658220302504.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n, khi\u1ebfn Hasebe kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1m theo ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. Meunier \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1eaft ngang v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lukaku. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u01a1 ch\u00e2n l\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt ra ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u00e1ng c\u1ef1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tan bi\u1ebfn. Chadli \u0111\u00e3 b\u0103ng l\u00ean v\u1eeba k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf cho B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c gi\u00e2y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. <br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274945/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"846","checkdouble":"190257"},{"date":"10:31 03/07","title":"Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Dalic tin t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/an-tuong-kieu-chao-cua-chien-binh-dzyuba.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi London ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Alisson Becker v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay Courtois ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London, <strong>v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Madrid n\u1eefa</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c con t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Madrid, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n ch\u00fang. B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 <strong>t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Courtois cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, khi h\u1ecd l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, khi anh ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Casemiro v\u00e0 Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid tr\u1edf n\u00ean g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"845","checkdouble":"190258"},{"date":"10:49 03/07","title":"Vieira: \"Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/vieira-phap-se-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Vieira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Uruguay.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Vieira-tin-tuong-Phap-se-vao-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Vieira cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u1eabu sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta h\u01a1i kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m nay\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Brazil ho\u1eb7c B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-phap-trai-long-ve-sieu-pham-cuu-roi-chien-thang-argentina-421-190134.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"844","checkdouble":"190260"},{"date":"11:08 03/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 La Masia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Robert Navarro c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</h2><h2>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Navarro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Monaco \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMonaco l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro t\u1eeb Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Monaco \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n h\u1ebft. Kylian Mbappe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Paris Saint-Germain. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy \u0111\u1ec1u gia nh\u1eadp Manchester City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Thomas Lemar, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-liverpool-bat-ngo-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-tien-ve-fabinho-tu-monaco-172-187236.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n cho Liverpool</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Monaco \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. H\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Willem Geubbels t\u1eeb Lyon\u00a0 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Samuel Grandsir c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRobert Navarro l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stade Louis II h\u00e8 2018. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t la tinh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Navarro c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cRobertinho\u201d \u1edf l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o La Masia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Monaco:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia La Liga ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Thomas Lemar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-khung-monaco-180-187985.html\">Barca gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao kh\u1ee7ng Monaco</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"843","checkdouble":"190262"},{"date":"11:04 03/07","title":"Courtois n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi London ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Alisson Becker v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay Courtois ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London, <strong>v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Madrid n\u1eefa</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c con t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Madrid, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n ch\u00fang. B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 <strong>t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Courtois cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, khi h\u1ecd l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, khi anh ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Casemiro v\u00e0 Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid tr\u1edf n\u00ean g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"842","checkdouble":"190264"},{"date":"11:50 03/07","title":"Hazard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 qu\u00e1 d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ebf t\u1eafc to\u00e0n t\u1eadp, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o. Ch\u1ec9 khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn 2 g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1, HLV Roberto Martinez m\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadt may, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacer Chadli v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 65, v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c. Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi B\u1ec9 b\u1ecb x\u1ee9 Wales lo\u1ea1i \u1edf EURO 2016. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110T B\u1ec9\" title=\"Marouane Fellaini ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a gi\u00fap tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ph\u1ea1t tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. B\u1edfi v\u1eady ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch &ndash; \u0110T Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Martinez c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110T B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"841","checkdouble":"190265"},{"date":"11:30 03/07","title":"HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 d\u1ecda d\u1eabm ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \"trong c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 c\u00e1i \u0111en\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/013720-3.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1eafng thua c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Vladimir Petkovic c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">Tr\u1eadn thua \u201cc\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Anh \u201c\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec v\u00e0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u01b0\u1edbi tay ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i chung k\u1ebft \u0111ang t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf cho Tam S\u01b0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t mang t\u00ean Colombia \u0111\u00eam nay.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/013720-3.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ef1 tin g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho Anh \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, Anh s\u1ebd tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Vladimir Petkovic \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng d\u1ecda d\u1eabm ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh r\u1eb1ng \u201ch\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2u!\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 55 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ed1c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169: \u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai coi th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">D\u00f9 sao \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1eafng m\u1eaft ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Petkovic \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 64 n\u0103m, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 1954 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thuy-dien-vs-thuy-sy-21h00-ngay-37-chia-khoa-o-hang-thu-421-190249.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (21h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7): C\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn tay, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea5t?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#111111\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"840","checkdouble":"190266"},{"date":"11:09 03/07","title":"Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch t\u1ef1a tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a Neymar trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil 2-0 Mexico \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">Neymar ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng khi in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/brazil-20-mexico-xung-danh-nguoi-dan-duong-cua-world-cup-421-190244.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brazil h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Mexico</span> \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao PSG c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u00e0n k\u1ecbch k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Miguel Layun \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1i gi\u1eabm ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn anh l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n \u0103n v\u1ea1 t\u1ecf v\u1ebb \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 coi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico b\u1ecb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch gay g\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico b\u1ecb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch gay g\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Neymar-lan-lon-tren-duong-pitch.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Sau nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 HLV Juan Carlos Osorio v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Miguel Layun b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ngay-hom-nay-37-469-190269.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico</span>. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer m\u1ec9a mai s\u00e2u cay: \u201cNeymar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i! Th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1eadu ta tr\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 coi v\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u1ea3, t\u1eeb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u1eadu ta c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u0103n ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng? B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, hay c\u00f3 khi c\u1eadu ta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1eafm sao?\u201d \u2013 C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh Neymar th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0103n v\u1ea1. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 anh vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i quan t\u00e2m khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Brazil v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u1ecd tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-tinh-bo-truoc-moi-cao-buoc-an-va-421-190251.html\">Neymar t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0103n v\u1ea1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-neymar-khi-thien-than-luc-ac-quy-421-190242.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Neymar \u2013 Khi thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n, l\u00fac \u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u2026</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#111111\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#111111\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"839","checkdouble":"190267"},{"date":"11:40 03/07","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 3/7: Maradona khuy\u00ean h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Neymar t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/ngay-hom-nay-37.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (3/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Maradona khuy\u00ean h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Neymar t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a PSG ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf: &quot;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0103n v\u1ea1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi VAR \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Neymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean d\u00f9 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfm khuy\u1ebft, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Neymar v\u1eabn n\u00ean thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i suy ngh\u0129 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, \u0111\u1eebng n\u00ean \u0103n v\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 l\u1ed9 li\u1ec5u n\u1eefa&quot;.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/anh6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">neymar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-tinh-bo-truoc-moi-cao-buoc-an-va-421-190251.html\">Neymar t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0103n v\u1ea1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marcus Rashford th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, anh khao kh\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai, 4/7. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, HLV Gareth Southgate s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Raheem Sterling tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, c\u00f2n Rashford ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<h2>Cavani \u0111i kh\u1eadp khi\u1ec5ng, d\u1ec5 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Esportes \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i r\u1ea5t kh\u1eadp khi\u1ec5ng. Theo b\u00e1o Goal, m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra s\u00e1ng 2/7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Oscar Tabarez c\u1ee7a Uruguay t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng cho Cavani. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. V\u1eeba qua, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p c\u1eaft l\u1edbp cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG b\u1ecb &quot;ph\u00f9 n\u1ec1 b\u00ean trong b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i&quot;.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/anh4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Casemiro v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Real Madrid d\u00ednh th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau pha ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Lozano c\u1ee7a Mexico \u1edf ph\u00fat 59. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Casemiro \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil d\u00ednh th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, tr\u1eadn thua l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&quot;, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Nishino chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9 d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Akira Nishino c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina &quot;tr\u1ea3m&quot; Sampaoli gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u00e0o th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c th\u1ee9 N\u0103m tu\u1ea7n  n\u00e0y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Argentina Claudio Tapia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi HLV  Jorge Sampaoli. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t  th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng  v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sevilla sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m  h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"838","checkdouble":"190269"},{"date":"07:52 03/07","title":"Su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup. </h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhat Ban lap ky luc voi ban thang cua Haraguchi vao luoi DT Bi.\" title=\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2002. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2002 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. T\u00e1m n\u0103m sau, &quot;samurai xanh&quot; c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Paraguay v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0 v\u00e0 thua 3-5 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup c\u00f3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini v\u00e0 Nacer Chadli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Opta ph\u00e2n t\u00edch s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u World Cup m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1966, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen l\u00e0 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1 ly xa nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (18.6) m\u00e9t.</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Takashi Inui. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\">M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1c khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c danh th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00ecm n\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Rivaldo khi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002. \u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (s\u00e2n Kobe Wing, Kobe).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1996. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-3 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 1966. Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 ch\u1ec9 sau 25 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"837","checkdouble":"190240"},{"date":"07:22 03/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274945/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00f3t tim</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i d\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ai \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 World Cup c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u00e1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Rostov Arena \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 2 (2/7). M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn &ldquo;t\u00ed hon&rdquo; Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eabn \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch B\u1ec9 2-0 sau 7 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o l\u00fac tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd thua d\u1ec5 bao nhi\u00eau th\u00ec g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u0169ng ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau v\u1edbi 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng (ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 22 gi\u00e2y), Nacer Chadli k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Du-am-Bi-3-2-Nhat-Ban-Quy-do-no-Samurai-loi-cam-on!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 ph\u00fat, Genki Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Sau \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina, T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed3i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean trong g\u1ea7n 70 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua. Ch\u00fa th\u1ecf ham ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua r\u00f9a, nh\u01b0ng &ldquo;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i &ldquo;Samurai xanh&rdquo;. Vertonghen, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ed9c l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 2-1 ph\u00fat 69 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhat Ban dan truoc Bi 2-0\" title=\"Nhat Ban dan truoc Bi 2-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Nhat-Ban-dan-truoc-Bi-2-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn 2-0 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n5 ph\u00fat sau, Eden Hazard xoay tr\u1edf kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t ng\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ec3 Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u1ec9 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng. Qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00fa nh\u1ea5c ch\u00e2n t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chadli d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho B\u1ec9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00e1c. Sau hi\u1ec7p 1, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. V\u00e0 khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n cho 30 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi vuot qua Nhat vao tu ket\" title=\"Bi vuot qua Nhat vao tu ket\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sai. Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn cho t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 v\u1eabn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 l\u1eebng kh\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 h\u01a1n 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u1ea5t h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c. Suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i theo B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ecbu 2 b\u00e0n thua n\u1eb7ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a v\u00f5 s\u0129 quy\u1ec1n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tinh than Bi co van de\" title=\"tinh than Bi co van de\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/tinh-than-Bi-co-van-de.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ee7 quan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh World Cup 2018, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i t\u1edbi VCK, B\u1ec9 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez may m\u1eafn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng &ldquo;nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u&rdquo; Gibraltar, \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp r\u1ed3i Estonia \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Hy L\u1ea1p, Bosnia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi Nga (th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 1, h\u01a1n ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi VCK, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 Martinez kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ra th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u01b0a d\u1ed1c l\u00f2ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00eam 2/7, d\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi d\u1ea1y cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc th\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan. Khi trong \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi vs Nhat Lukaku va Kagawa\" title=\"Bi vs Nhat Lukaku va Kagawa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Bi-vs-Nhat-Lukaku-va-Kagawa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 t\u1ec9nh gi\u1ea5c. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n t\u1eeb HLV Martinez trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Th\u1eadt may l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra: B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 Brazil?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa, ngay 1h ng\u00e0y 7/7 t\u1edbi th\u00f4i, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c C\u0110V B\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc r\u00fat ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. \u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng Samurai xanh b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Bi 3-2 Nhat Ban\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thong-so-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"836","checkdouble":"190243"},{"date":"07:16 03/07","title":"Willian cay c\u00fa khi Brazil b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/willian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao ch\u01a1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs Mexico khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Willian-phat-bieu-ve-Brazil-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Mexico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Brazil b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Sau \u0111\u00f3 khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Selecao co \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ed3n \u00e9p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brazil, song c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Selecao \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico song Brazil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf samba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao ch\u01a1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian duoc khen ngoi boi tro ly DT Brazil, Sylvinho sau tran thang Mexico.\" title=\"Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Brazil, Sylvinho sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/willian-brazil-can-bang-trong-tan-cong-va-phong-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00ec s\u1ebd r\u00f5. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Brazil x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Neymar m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/willian-duoc-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-cua-dt-brazil-465-190225.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sylvinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Willian</span>, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Tite \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"835","checkdouble":"190246"},{"date":"07:02 03/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (3/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-372018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold